description:
Clint Barton (aka Hawkeye) plays a game of Wii Sports Resort Archery, but things suddenly go haywire in Wuhu Island...

Special thanks to DitzyFlama, Contendo, Free Boredom, RainbowKappa, and Paniaal for their editing advice and review. Appreciate you all!

Check out the VFX Breakdown of this video! https://youtu.be/88W1SOAYmmU

Join the DISCORD! https://discord.gg/3mQtUPGfzG

---

Software Used:
Adobe After Effects - https://www.adobe.com/products/aftereffects
Adobe Premiere Pro - https://www.adobe.com/products/premiere
Adobe Photoshop - https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop
Nuke Studio (Non-commercial license) - https://www.foundry.com/products/nuke-family/non-commercial
Blender - https://www.blender.org/
Mixamo - https://www.mixamo.com/
CamTrackAR - https://fxhome.com/blog/camtrackar-help-guide
Dolphin - https://dolphin-emu.org/
BrawlCrate - https://github.com/soopercool101/BrawlCrate
Switch Toolbox - https://github.com/KillzXGaming/Switch-Toolbox

Plug-ins Used:
Mirror_Texture_Node_Group by Tryptech (to fix broken UVs)
Light-Wrap Generator by ProductionCrate https://news.productioncrate.com/easy-light-wrap-script-for-after-effects/
Export Composition Data to JSON - https://gachokistudios.com/how-to-transfer-camera-tracking-data-from-after-effects-to-blender/

3D Sources (in order):
Wuhu Island - https://www.reddit.com/r/wii/comments/q20pg9/i_ported_wuhu_island_to_blender/
Default Mii (Miitomo) - https://www.models-resource.com/mobile/miitomo/model/30547/
Pilotwings Resort Game Banner - https://www.models-resource.com/3ds/pilotwingsresort/model/33353/
Everything else was ripped straight from Wii Sports Resort using BrawlCrate

Visual Sources:
The Avengers (2012)
Hawkeye (2021)
